name: Vladimir
description_short: Russia's enigmatic leader, with a poker face
description_full: that could make a mime jealous and a knack for keeping the world guessing. Love him or scratch your head in confusion, one thing's for sure: he's a master of political intrigue and a source of endless memes.

name: Oleg
description_short: A Russian billionaire, the dark wizard
description_full: behind the scenes of RusAl, a giant in the aluminum industry. With his criminal past and barbaric privatization of early 90s he has a talent to survive in complex political landscape of Russia.

name: Oleksandr
description_full: the ring mastermind who conquered the world with his fists. From Olympic glory to heavyweight fame.

name: Milla
description_full: model, and singer, Milla Jovovich is a global icon with a heart of gold. Her public support for Ukraine during the Russian invasion has been unwavering, and her charity work has raised millions for humanitarian aid.

name: Joe
description_short: The POTUS, being involved in scandals related to Ukraine.
